    <h3>Adaptation notes</h3>
    <p>The source chapter states the foundational assumptions of microbial growth and derives the growth laws, then builds toward mechanistic coarse-grained models linking gene expression to growth. We use the smallest coupled-sector model that reproduces the qualitative law (ribosome fraction rising with nutrient quality) as a runnable follow-through on Chapter 1. The formal derivations and the link to the experimental growth laws are in the source.</p>

